    {
      "text": "%spark_user.pyspark\n\"\"\"\nSOH Stress Factor XGBoost 모델(v2)\n\n주요 기능:\n- XGBoost + SHAP을 이용한 daily SOH 변수 중요도 분석 \n- SHAP 절대값 평균 -\u003e 정규화 -\u003e 로그스케일로 변환하여 상대적 중요도 계산\n- SOH 주요 영향변수 및 영향도(스트레스 지수) 계산\n- 영향변수 : accum_cycle_cnt(누적 주행(방전) 사이클 수), avg_bat_temp(배터리 온도), discharge_rate(방전률), daily_avg_dod(일일 평균 방전량), \n-           volt_response_idx(배터리(전압)반응성 지수), sob(전압균형지수), sot(온도균형지수), driving_behavior_idx(주행 습관 지수)\n- update : 결과데이터셋 구조 변경(\u002725.10.31) - ID, day_of_soh, daily_soh, longterm_soh, feature_value(배열), feature_importance(배열) 로 저장\n- id, day_of_soh 파라미터 입력으로 변경\n\"\"\"\n# 필요한 라이브러리 임포트\nimport os\nimport sys\nsys.path.append(\"/home/kadap/QH/SOH_Model\")\nimport pandas as pd\nfrom kslab_soh_config import STRESS_FACTOR_IO_CONFIG, DB_QUERY_FROM_SOH_FINAL, DB_QUERY_FROM_SOH_CAPA, MLP_IO_CONFIG\nfrom kslab_soh_utils import setup_spark_session, load_data_from_csv, load_data_from_db, save_results_to_csv, save_results_to_db,load_data_from_parquet\nfrom pyspark.sql import SparkSession\nfrom pyspark.sql.functions import col, avg, stddev, exp, pow, round, corr, lag, when, abs as spark_abs, lpad\nimport matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n#import seaborn as sns\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom sklearn.preprocessing import MinMaxScaler, StandardScaler\nimport xgboost as xgb\nimport shap\nimport warnings\nfrom pyspark.sql.window import Window\n#from gplearn.genetic import SymbolicRegressor\nfrom pyspark.sql.types import StructType, StructField, StringType, DoubleType, BooleanType\nfrom sklearn.metrics import mean_squared_error, r2_score\nfrom sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split\nimport joblib\nimport logging\nwarnings.filterwarnings(\u0027ignore\u0027)\n\nimport numpy as np\n# numpy 2.x에서 삭제된 alias를 shap용으로 복원\nif not hasattr(np, \"int\"):\n    np.int \u003d int\nif not hasattr(np, \"bool8\"):\n    np.bool8 \u003d np.bool_\n\nimport shap\nprint(\"numpy :\", np.__version__)\nprint(\"shap  :\", shap.__version__)\n\n# 로깅 설정\nlogging.basicConfig(\n    level\u003dlogging.INFO,\n    format\u003d\u0027%(asctime)s - %(levelname)s - %(message)s\u0027\n)\nlogger \u003d logging.getLogger(__name__)",
