      "text": "%spark_user.pyspark\ndef save_stress_overwrite(spark, final_df):\n    out_path \u003d STRESS_FACTOR_IO_CONFIG[\u0027output\u0027][\u0027parquet_path\u0027]\n\n    (\n        final_df\n            .write\n            .mode(\"overwrite\")\n            .partitionBy(\"deviceId\")\n            .parquet(out_path)\n    )\n\n    logger.info(f\"[SAVE] deviceId 기준 partition 저장 완료: {out_path}\")\n",
